comments: Exemplary!! Prof. Jernigan teaches applicable skills using a hands-on approach. He wants students to understand the value of being resourceful, so he uses a discussion board to allow them to help each other and awards extra-credit for participation. He actively participates as well and is accessible via email and text messaging. Highly recommend!

comments: Amazing professor. Shares lot\'s of real life example. Can text him anytime, and he\'ll reply in less than 30 minutes. Always there for you. Lots of homework, but he guides you through them step by step in a video simulation. Will tell you what to expect on the test. It is a hard class overall so put in a lot of effort. Offers extra credit.
